text: Ibrahim Mustapha (born 1 September 1996) is a Nigerian international footballer who plays for Dibba Al-Hisn] as a striker. ==Career== Born in Maiduguri, he has played club football for El-Kanemi Warriors, Enyimba, Gombe United, Plateau United and Dibba Al-Hisn.
